^{"statusCode_description":"Indicates attempted access to an unreachable or non-existing resource like e.g. an unknown topic or partition. GET requests to endpoints not allowed in the accesslists will also result in this response."}
^{"statusCode_description":"Indicates that a rate limit threshold has been reached, and the client should retry again later."}
^{"statusCode_description":"A server-side problem that might not be addressable from the client side. Retriable Kafka errors will contain error code 50003 in the response body."}
